mplcursors – Interactive data selection cursors for Matplotlib
==============================================================

|PyPI| |Read the Docs| |Travis| |CodeCov|

.. |PyPI|
   image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/mplcursors.svg
   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/mplcursors
